3-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-236\" src=\"https://lqustg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_7003-2-300x198.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"309\" height=\"203\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[title size=\"1\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single solid\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Deer Park Location[/title]\r\n[one_half last=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3022.182254844767!2d-73.34743100000003!3d40.758016000000005!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89e82c6a752548a3%3A0x52cd8cf3285cb4f6!2s519+Acorn+St%2C+Deer+Park%2C+NY+11729!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1433354182484\" width=\"100%\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>[/one_half]\r\n[one_half last=\"yes\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n\r\n[title size=\"3\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single solid\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Address:[/title]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333;\">519 Acorn St</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333;\"> Deer Park, NY 11729</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong>Phone-</strong> 631-676-2436</span>\r\n\r\n[/one_half]','Deer Park','','publish','closed','closed','','deer-park','','','2019-07-02 18:58:41','2019-07-02 18:58:41','',0,'https://lqustg.wpengine.com/?page_id=17',0,'page','',0),(19,6,'2014-12-17 18:59:05','2014-12-17 18:59:05','<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-240 alignleft\" src=\"https://lqustg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_7013-2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"291\" height=\"219\" />Located in the heart of Hells Kitchen, our NYC showroom is filled with furniture. Apart from the sea of samples within the showroom, we have our drapery staff, soft goods and upholsterers. The city showroom is a showcase of custom craftsmanship in the heart of a bustling city. It is a gem and the best in the decorating and related fields know where to go for long lasting, heirloom quality furniture. These qualities will add value to wherever they are destined to go. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">With so many styles and forms to choose from, a friendly staff, and dedicated service, please schedule an appointment today and see everything in person.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">A very important note:<img class=\" wp-image-239 alignright\" src=\"https://lqustg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_7018-2-300x205.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"219\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">In both our showrooms you will meet a dedicated Quintana family member who will guide and help as thoroughly as they can in the upholstery process. There is no salesperson or middleman to worry about. We do this because we are responsible for everything that leaves the workroom and stand behind our products. It is the only way we know how to conduct business. It is an old school way but it works for us.</span>\r\n\r\n[title size=\"1\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single solid\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]New York City Location[/title][one_half last=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]<iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3982.9298573339784!2d-73.9972322939077!3d40.76234358811926!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c2584e6356f6db%3A0x57efc1c307892f96!2s599+11th+Ave%2C+New+York%2C+NY+10036!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1441120581406\" width=\"359\" height=\"359\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>[/fusion_text][/one_half][one_half last=\"yes\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text] [/fusion_text][title size=\"3\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single solid\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Address:[/title][fusion_text]<span style=\"color: #333333;\">599 11th Ave </span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333;\"> New York, NY 10036</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong>Phone-</strong> 212-462-2033</span>[/fusion_text][/one_half]','NYC','','publish','