from Manhattan to Montauk and beyond. A very good reference to our work can be seen in Amanda Nisbet’s book <i>Dazzling Design.</i></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #333333;\"> We can create custom coffee tables and shelved tables. We also make tailored skirts for entry tables, halls and vanities. We upholster walls as well. LQU does it all when it comes to carpentry and upholstery so go ahead and contact us and see what we can do for you!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"p1\">To Contact our warehouse in Brooklyn, NY\r\nCall: Clarisa\r\n1-718-827-3240</h2>\r\n<div class=\"\"></div>','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2019-07-02 19:02:21','2019-07-02 19:02:21','',0,'https://lqustg.wpengine.com/?page_id=24',0,'page','',0),(26,6,'2014-12-17 19:01:53','2014-12-17 19:01:53',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','',26,'','','2015-06-09 13:11:10','2015-06-09 13:11:10','',0,'https://lqustg.wpengine.com/?p=26',15,'nav_menu_item','',0),(28,6,'2014-12-17 19:01:52','2014-12-17 19:01:52',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','',28,'','','2015-06-09 13:11:10','2015-06-09 13:11:10','',0,'https://lqustg.wpengine.com/?p=28',12,'nav_menu_item','',0),(29,6,'2014-12-17 19:01:52','2014-12-17 19:01:52',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','',29,'','','2015-06-09 13:11:10','2015-06-09 13:11:10','',0,'https://lqustg.wpengine.com/?p=29',11,'nav_menu_item','',0),(31,6,'2014-12-17 19:01:50','2014-12-17 19:01:50',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','',31,'','','2015-06-09 13:11:10','2015-06-09 13:11:10','',0,'https://lqustg.wpengine.com/?p=31',9,'nav_menu_item','',0),(32,6,'2014-12-17 19:01:49','2014-12-17 19:01:49',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','',32,'','','2015-06-09 13:11:06','2015-06-09 13:11:06','',0,'https://lqustg.wpengine.com/?p=32',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(33,6,'2014-12-17 19:01:48','2014-12-17 19:01:48',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','',33,'','','2015-06-09 13:11:06','2015-06-09 13:11:06','',0,'https://lqustg.wpe